      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The exterior has a few minor scratches and small chips, but no major dents or damage. The interior is well-maintained with some light signs of use on the seats. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been regularly serviced.",
      "price": 35000.0,
